s of whether they are receiving an acetylcholinesterase inhibitor.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/87657/', '', 'Ginkgo biloba, Aducanumab', 'Tetracaine, Ketotifen, Levocetirizine, Cetirizine, Trimethobenzamide, Azelastine', 1767369485);
